Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A way of expressing gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I can sense that\NI am needed elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:05.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my way of repaying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Did I really lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.82,Main,,0,0,0,,But how many would bind him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,with a scarf made\Nwith embedded wires?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:12.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:13.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NShe's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:59.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's\Nfinally the season, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:03.71,Main,,0,0,0,,The season when\Nit's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Any month now my heating\Nbill will finally decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Just me, or is anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,having a bit of a\Ndéjà vu moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NIt's almost Valentines!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,That's an extremely\Nimportant day, y'know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,A day meant for\Ngorging on chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] That's not\Nactually what it's about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA thinking]\NDefinitely a déjà vu moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.23,Main,,0,0,0,,So, Yoko, what are your plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll give\Nchocolate to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, no... I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] It doesn't have\Nto be anything romantic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:33.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You can give someone chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,just 'cause you're\Nthankful to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:38.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. A way of\Nexpressing gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Something happened\Nthe other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[mewling sounds]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww... That poor kitty...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think he can\Nget down all by himself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But... what should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's really high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,,And I don't know if that\Ntree will take my weight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.94,Main,,0,0,0,,if I try to climb it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:11.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Still... I need to\Nrescue it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] I can sense that\NI am urgently needed elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I have more important\Nthings to do than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NMore important than cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:20.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NHe dropped everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,rushed right over to\Nhelp me rescue the cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:23.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh... That kinda\Nseems like something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.16,Main,,0,0,0,,that should've happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] So, anyway,\Nwhat happened to the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.88,Main,,0,0,0,,We got it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,...but it ran away\Nbefore I had the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,to pet it or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NThat's how the story ends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,That's all you can offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, forgive me if I\Ncouldn't meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] I wonder if it\Nwill come back to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The cat, repay me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know,\Nthe thing from stories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.48,Main,,0,0,0,,where animals repay\Npeople who help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely certain\Nwhat a grateful kitten
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,would look like, but it sounds\Nrather adorable, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWell, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh? Uh-huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThanks for the help, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:03.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I got you some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NEr, salmon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThank you for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I got you some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NAs a sign of my gratitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose I will let\Nyou stroke my paw pads
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,just this once, fortunate human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Doesn't sound like a\Nvery grateful cat if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Where's Yamaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. He's probabl--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I am at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs]\NI have a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yes...? Go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Well...\Nthis might sound... weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,...but if the kitten comes\Nback... to repay you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,...do me a favor...? Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Capture the moment on this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:50.50,Main,,0,0,0,,so that it can be\Nimmortalized for all eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NI'm not sure I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NPlease, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[BEL]\NTeru. Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Bel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks a lot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:20.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been a great human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful to you\Nfor taking me in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:25.49,Main,,0,0,0,,and looking out for me.\NYou've been so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.62,Main,,0,0,0,,So, here... Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my way of repaying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That felt like Bel\Nwas saying goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,and leaving and\Nnever coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, cause of that\Nstory Yoko told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Still... it was\Njust a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NOh, um... thanks, Bel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so that was my morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You see, it's just\Nlike the stories say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Bel repayed you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Of course, cats\Nshow love very differently
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,than humans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.32,Main,,0,0,0,,And... I guess your\Nability to receive that love
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:08.49,Main,,0,0,0,,is a good measure of\Nyour success as a pet owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Hey, if anyone\Nknows about pets, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYou're a model pet owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh come on,\Nyou've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Just because she likes animals
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,doesn't make her\Na good pet owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,There's more to it than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there is a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,that you can teach me\Nin that department...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sweet one must have\Ngiven you so many gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] Uh?!\NOf course she has!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.14,Main,,0,0,0,,But the only gift that really\Nmatters to me in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.14,Main,,0,0,0,,is having Eternal by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know who could\Nask for more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's all calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You could have a competition\Nto see who cats like more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] You're all\Nabout kitty pictures, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,So why don't we just agree
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,that whoever takes\Nthe better picture wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NCome on, Bel... Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait...! No...! Hold on...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.39,Main,,0,0,0,,We can snuggle later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,My wrists were about to collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,from holding this\Ncamera for hours
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,and now suddenly,\Nthey feel completely healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I worship you, Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.96,Main,,0,0,0,,How'm I supposed to pick one\Nwhen they're all so cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's freakin' impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NI brought my picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NMe too. This is my best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,The three of us will\Nbe in charge of judging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWell, they are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NYeah they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Both kitties are adorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,but... it's a bit like comparing\Ntwo peas from the same pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That obviously isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess Beelzebub\Nis pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Eternal is, too,\Nso I can see why
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,they'd have a hard time\Npicking just one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.38,Main,,0,0,0,,D'you think I could keep this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,How about we\Njust make it a trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA sighs]\NI honestly don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,if I'll ever\Nunderstand cat lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Some competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.77,Main,,0,0,0,,That was nothing but a\Nbig waste of time if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I got a cute new kitty\Npicture out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'd say it went fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! If it's a competition\Nyou're looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba Odagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,We've got a volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsuji alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Lemme guess:\Nyou're here to challenge me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,to an eating competition...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Not this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.29,Main,,0,0,0,,cause today I'm gonna be\Nthe one challenging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.04,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Whaddaya say\Nto jumbo hamburgers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME]\NUh... You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No fair! They wouldn't\Neven let me sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I take it this was\None of the places
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,that had the good\Nsense to ban you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:17.81,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You had actually forgotten that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:24.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME] Ha ha ha! They let\Nme in no questions asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe that would make\Nme the winner by default.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME]\NTsuji 1... Odagiri zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! You suck! Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hehe! Woo-hoo...! Boo-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Did... I really lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's think about\Nthis for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NHey, you're right, Hayama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.92,Main,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let me in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,because I'm a bigger\Nthreat to them than he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:50.67,Main,,0,0,0,,and therefore that makes me\Nthe winner by default...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop dancing, you little monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,So... I suppose some\Ncongratulations are in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I recognize you...\NWhat's your name again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Errrr... Nishi-something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand\Nhow you would know my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Technically,\Nhe only knows half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It's "Nishikawa"...!\NTo you that's Miss Nishikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Never forget to\Nuse the honorific...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You'd better learn\Nto show some respect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,to your superiors, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji...! Be quiet right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? That is a cool trick...\NJust like Sasame told me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Right... you know\Nher from your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.13,Main,,0,0,0,,She told me that you're one\Nof her friends from class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME] Well, anyway,\Nthanks for looking out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,She can be kinda\Nfragile sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...! Well,\NI don't think... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:38.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy she thinks\Nof me as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI gasps and thinks]\NThat smile! I may go blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME]\NSasame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess what...!\NI won against Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't call that winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't win if the other\Nperson doesn't enter the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuh-huh...!\NThere were witnesses;
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,that friend of yours\Neven congratulated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You know... that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:06.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishi... hara...? Kawa...?\NSomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Yoko Nishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it, she's\Nthe one I talked to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\NI was totally polite
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.42,Main,,0,0,0,,and told her thanks for\Nlooking out for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[SASAME]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds pretty mature, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep... Just like a\Nbig brother should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You are you such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez...! How could\Nyou say something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,so embarrassing like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet you made her feel super\Nawkward and uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Think it's a normal thing\Nto say for most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[SASAME] Maybe if we'd been\Nfriends for a really long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like Nishikawa and I\Nare childhood friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,so we're not nearly\Nthat close yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME]\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiot...! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,She's going to think\NI'm a total loser now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get why it's such\Na big deal. Just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NHelp me here, I need ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,When I give him the\Nchocolates, I want it to be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:54.71,Main,,0,0,0,,the most memorable experience\Nthat he's ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Not asking for much, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much\Nchocolate I can buy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,with my allowance this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been dreaming\Nabout this for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA] Hello, we're\Ntalking about me, not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:05.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I think if you\Nknitted him a scarf
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.77,Main,,0,0,0,,and made some\Nchocolates from scratch,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,that would be pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Really?\NDon't plenty of people do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But how many would\Nbind him with a scarf made
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,with embedded wires and then\Nforce-feed him chocolates
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,drugged with an exceptionally\Npowerful aphrodisiac?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,They aren't serious, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NI have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of\Npreparations to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NCareful walking home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm off to trap my man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] That sounds\Nlike quite an elaborate plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the young\Nmaster will be surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,He's in for a\Nlovely Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.59,Main,,0,0,0,,And... I have\Nalso been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,This Valentine's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe I would like\Nto make chocolates as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry could you\Nsay that again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,My hearing seems\Nto be a little bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I said chocolates...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to attempt\Nmaking chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I think I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You wish to stockpile it\Nfor emergency rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NNo, for Valentine's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:06.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And may I ask who will be the\Nrecipient of said chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,There's my friends, of\Ncourse, and I'd like to send
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,a whole mountain of\Nthem to my father, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:13.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What were we\Ntalking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NValentine's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I've decided that I am going\Nto try to make chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:21.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Good... This time of year\Nis as busy as Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'll gladly take\Nall the help I can get,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,even if it comes from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean make\Nthem for the shop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to create\Ndelicious chocolates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.23,Main,,0,0,0,,and give them to the people\Nin my life I'm thankful for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It won't interfere with\Nmy duties here, I promise
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO thinking] Miss Yoko\Nmaking chocolates from scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll start out\Nenergetically enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,But disaster will strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.70,Main,,0,0,0,,and she'll wind up\Nexhausting herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Then she'll end up sick\Nin bed, unable to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'll be understaffed at\Nthe busiest time of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThat's my situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, say you'll help...!\NI'll be lost without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.92,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,And I don't see why\Nyou want me so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't you just\Nask somebody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like you're\Nthe perfect person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,for the job, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:04.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I'm assuming\Nyou don't have any plans
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.39,Main,,0,0,0,,for valentine's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you're insulting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat are you doing here, Sonobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NI was asking Nishiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,if she would give me\Na hand at the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh, pick me! I can help.\NI know how to do everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,and you won't have\Nto pay me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You can compensate\Nme with cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,If I do that, there\Nwon't be any more goods
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.78,Main,,0,0,0,,to sell to the customers,\Nso I have to pay you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine... suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:30.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I would\Nappreciate your help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I'm willing to do it\Nas long as I don't have to wear
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,that maid getup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... I don't know, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,it's kinda like a "my house,\Nmy rules" situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:48.39,Main,,0,0,0,,All right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Is everybody ready\Nto sell some cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NPlease, Miss Yoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I really think you should\Nconserve your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHey! I thought we had a deal...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I wearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Oh, good...\NIt fits you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] This is a direct\Nviolation of our agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] As I recall,\Nyou said you did not wish
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,to wear this maid outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.99,Main,,0,0,0,,and so I made\Nyou a different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NCalm down, it looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NLovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I had really hoped\Nthat I would be able
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,to make some for\Nthe two of you, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.71,Main,,0,0,0,,...but I just\Ndidn't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know getting ready
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,for Valentine's Day\Nwas so intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I stayed up\Nforty-eight hours straight
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:25.80,Main,,0,0,0,,trying to make Hayama's\Nnew outfit for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! That's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:33.73,Main,,0,0,0,,As you can see,\Nwe are quite crowded today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,but I promise we will help\Neveryone as quickly as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWelcome to Secret Garden...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Please decide what\Nyou would like to order,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'll be happy to ring you up\Nright here once you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I still don't get\Nwhy she made me come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.11,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna need\Nall hands on deck today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Just look at how busy it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:49.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's that other guy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You know,\Nthe creepy butler dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NSorry, I can't help right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:56.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm busy making this special\Nchocolate cake for Miss Yoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,and I don't know how\Nmuch longer it's going to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:01.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That can wait 'til later...\NTell him, Sonobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:08.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NShe's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] She has been up\Nfor two days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,We need her help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,How can she sleep\Nwhen it's this busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NIt'll be alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,With you here, I'm sure\Nwe can pull through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely! Let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Secret Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NIt's almost too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThanks for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry... I expected you\Nto be busy... It's Valentine's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NThat's so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Awwww...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Man... I'm getting tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe! We need you to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on! Sonobe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Running out of steam already...?\NIt's a little early for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,If only I were\Nas tireless as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Too bad...!\NI've got hours left in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWell, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.52,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'm sure you won't mind\Nif I just take a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nishiyama. I know\NI can always count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO thinking] She could make\Nlife a lot easier on herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much,\Nand have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:19.66,Main,,0,0,0,,One limited edition\NGâteau Chocolat, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:22.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, one Gâteau Chocolat\Ncoming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:25.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the Tsuji twins again...!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop looking at me like that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys can buy cakes on\NValentine's Day too, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course they can!\NIt's totally no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:34.43,Main,,0,0,0,,There are lots of special,\Nlimited edition items
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,during Valentine's\Nand Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:39.77,Main,,0,0,0,,He saves up money especially\Nfor this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it's no big deal,\Nbut it's still a bit unusual;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet you get weird\Nlooks from some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:45.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME]\NI don't care...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I get plenty of chocolate\Nfrom girls at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,so it's not like\NI'm really worried
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:50.44,Main,,0,0,0,,about my reputation or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:52.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow... seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you look so\Nsurprised that he's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm even the mascot\Nfor my school club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:00.58,Main,,0,0,0,,How cool is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Way cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NThank you so much for coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:10.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope we'll see you again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NHey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I just\Ncouldn't pass up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.35,Main,,0,0,0,,the chance to see\Nyou hard at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a waste of time\Nto me, but suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] You could\Nstart working here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I could find\Na position for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NShe's awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... that's not really\Nmy thing, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA thinking]\NWhat's not her thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS]\NGoodbye! Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:41.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NListen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to thank all\Nof you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,for your hard work today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I would have been completely\Nlost without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,The best part of it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,after that nap I feel\Nabout ten years younger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO grunts]\NSonobe...! I could kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yesterday was exhausting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yknow, after seeing\Nyou in that maid outfit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I kinda wanna try one myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:11.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should ask Sonobe\Nif she would make one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.90,Main,,0,0,0,,That isn't gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko said she only seems to like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.99,Main,,0,0,0,,making people wear them\Nif they don't actually want to,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,which isn't too surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... sounds like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess that's why\NNishiyama's a maid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL STUDENT 11A]\NNishiyama... a maid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.46,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It was the uniform that she\Nasked me to wear, okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.96,Main,,0,0,0,,She didn't have anything\Nelse so what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I wasn't wearing\Nit because I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure... of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true, whether\Nyou believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I never want to wear\Nthat outfit again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, I would rather die.\NIt was totally hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I completely\Nagree...! I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:49.69,Main,,0,0,0,,it fit you well enough, but it\Nwasn't exactly flattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It might work for someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.32,Main,,0,0,0,,but you looked so\Nuncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,...that's probably the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,you always pick such\Nboring outfits. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know if I would\Ncall my clothes boring, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I dunno, I actually thought\Nit looked pretty cute on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:07.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh?! Uh... You're\Nalways making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I was being serious,\Nwhy'd she get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can blame her\Nfor being a little suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,It was so nice of you to\Nhelp out in the shop yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And I... I wanted\Nto say thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,For that and for\Neverything else you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:34.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd been hoping someone'd\Ngive me a bag of rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:37.78,Main,,0,0,0,,They're Valentine's Day truffles\Nthat I made from scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA and HAYAMA]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,They're filled with\Nall the gratitude I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,toward you for being my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:45.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Homemade truffles.\NThat's pretty ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] They're not\Nwhat I'd call "melty,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,but they're edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.51,Main,,0,0,0,,There, you see...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I can make some things\Nif I put my mind to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Well done, Yoko...\NQuite impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIs it melting at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.06,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Not so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOh, Tsuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a little\Nsomething... For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Chocolates...?\NAre they really for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:24.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... I hope you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:25.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[SASAME thinking]\NNishikawa gave me chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What should\NI give her in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I-I I don't know\Nhow to thank her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What would be appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[SASAME thinking]\NSomething really awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:40.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Like a puppy... or a car...\Nor a house, maybe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji... I made these for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,A beautiful girl made\Nchocolates for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I will put these on the\Nfamily altar immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:51.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you\Ncould just eat them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,There should be\Na big batch of them
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,arriving for father\Ntoday, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:57.86,Main,,0,0,0,,So I guess all of my\NValentine's work is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO thinking]\NWhat? That's it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That's all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:04.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO thinking]\NWhat about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:07.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get any\NValentine's Day chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] The next\N"Three Leaves, Three Colors"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,is the last episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:54.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Let's have\NMiss Yoko say the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.39,0:23:55.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOkay, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:58.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time is, "I Am\NGraduating from Bread Crusts."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:23:59.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.98,0:24:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWell, that's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:02.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:03.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt will!
